[google_search_input://<name>]
google_query = Query to search
google_tld = Which countries version of Google to utilise. Most entries from https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Country_code_top-level_domain should be valid
google_language = Search language to utilise. May provide different results. See lr query parameters as per https://sites.google.com/site/tomihasa/google-language-codes.
maximum_results = Maximum number of results to fetch.